      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks that makes me feel better. i didnt really want to go back to the clinic since it's gonna cost me another visit fee and it's just a tiny thing. for the ointment, is there a specific kind i should look for? and how many times a day should i be putting it on to make sure the infection doesn't get worse?",
